DESCRIPTION:That's okay. So if you use one of the lifts either by riversi
 de and go over the bridge or there's one on Cotterells. \nYou need to go
  into the plaza and I'm the second tallest building. If you come from th
 e bridge I'm on the left. \n\nThen there's a call button. You need to pr
 ess the arrow button up and scroll up to 58 and press call. \nAnd I'll b
 uzz you in. \nDon't try to press 58 and call it doesn't work. Don't know
  why. \nI'm on floor 9. \nCall me if you have a problem 07783487132
