 ised advice.\n\n\nIf you need to reschedule\, you can do so at the botto
 m of this email.\n\n\nCalls may be recorded for training and quality pur
 poses. We use digital transcription technology to process your consultat
 ion notes and letters.\n\n\nIf you require an interpreter\, please do no
 t use this booking link. Contact our customer service team through your 
 account so we can assist you.\n\nLocation: This is a Google Meet web con
 ference.\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or sma
 rtphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/2a164536-132b-4583-b249-8902be75fe
