DESCRIPTION:Dear Roberta\n\nI am pleased to confirm your interview at Zon
 e for the Experience Director role. Details are as follows: \n\nDate: We
 dnesday 17th October 2018\nTime: ​10:30am\nLocation: Western Transit She
 d \, 12-13 Stable Street \, London (UK) \, N1C 4AB​\nWebsite: https://ww
 w.zonedigital.com/uk/\n​\n\n\nYou will be meeting with Matthew Chokshi o
 ur Creative Director. The meeting should last an hour and it will consis
 t of chat about your experience and talking through your portfolio. Plea
 se review the job description attached and do some research into Zone.\n
 \nCan you please bring 2 of the following documents to the interview? We
  need to check them as a part of the screening process:\n\nbirth certifi
 cate\ndriving license\npassport\nnational ID card\nIf you have any quest
 ions please don't hesitate to contact me\, otherwise good luck with the 
 interview. \n\nPlease confirm your attendance. \n\nKind regards\,
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20181017T113000
DTSTAMP:20220910T202347Z
