DESCRIPTION:You will be meeting\n Jo (Chief Design Officer) and Vix (Lead
  Designer).\n \nThese are they\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/jo-simmons-8
 60121/\njo is an incredible talent\, brilliant mentor and lovely woman t
 oo – as you can see shes been with Friday for 8 years \, very much a lea
 der of design there.\n \nand vix – whom you spoke to last week\nhttps://
 www.linkedin.com/in/vixyoung/\n \nThey have said\nPart of the interview 
 will consist of a portfolio review. As well as seeing the end result we 
 are really interested in the full end to end process. So please prepare 
 the candidate to share\, for example\, research\, ways of working and de
 sign iterations for their projects and let us know if they will require 
 a laptop to be set up.
