BEGIN:VEVENT
CREATED:20240627T194228Z
DESCRIPTION:Transition Day   Thursday 11th July 2024\nWe are delighted to
  be inviting your child to join us at Thomas Coram on Thursday 11th July
  for transition day.\nYou should bring your child to Thomas Coram for ou
 r rolling soft start from 8.35   8.50 am in their current school uniform
 \, with a water bottle and sun hat.\n\nschool will be providing a packed
  lunch for them. Although\, they are welcome to bring their own packed l
 unch should they wish. During the week commencing 1st July\, we will sen
 d an email informing you of the class your child will be in. The class t
 eachers will then be out on the LKS2 playground when the children arrive
 . They will then be taken into their new classrooms.\nYou will need to c
 ollect your child at 2.30pm from the LKS2 playground . If you are not go
 ing to be collecting your child please email admin@thomascoram.herts.sch
 .uk stating who is authorised to collect your child. Please make the sub
 ject heading Transition Day Collection.
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20240711T143000
DTSTAMP:20240711T080800Z
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/London:20240711T083000
LAST-MODIFIED:20240711T080759Z
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Effie - TC transition day
UID:C54D1E37-B0D3-4A60-B9FF-DA9A8383BD54
X-APPLE-CREATOR-IDENTITY:com.apple.mobilecal
END:VEVENT
